判頭唔好收咁貴"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:38:22.000Z","msg":"唔係地盤人工貴<br />\n係其他行業人工低造成錯覺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T06:17:34.000Z","msg":"有d行業又唔使知識<br />\n又唔使勞力<br />\n<br />\n低薪其實合理"},{"pid":"9552d72c01aeb385cf2de7906064c58b9fca490d","tid":1152213,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T09:20:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cpleung826.blogspot.com/2018/08/blog-post_15.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcpleung826.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F08%2Fblog-post_15.html&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=8f46f19a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cpleung826.blogspot.com/2018/08/blog-post_15.html</a><br />\n<br />\n其實R&amp;P係十分聰明既做法<br />\n如果比小蠔灣塊地港鐡建類似日出康城規模既市區<br />\n所得3000億用以津貼10條新綫其實幾好<br />\n<br />\n港鐵與政府都較想走R+P的玩法，批出將會有鐵路到達的「爛地皮」，讓港鐵把「爛地皮」變靚地，賣樓補貼，以後所有風險由港鐵承擔，亦不用受太多公眾監督。問題是如何令公眾重新接受這個模式呢？只要令公眾感覺政府funding這個模式經常會出事，而R+P的模式就無事，這不是很好的理據嗎？只要港鐵以R+P的項目做得特別好，政府funding的項目做得特別差，到時重推R+P模式就容易多了。"},{"pid":"e9caa9010410e5a611549643da3859e7f97b5471","tid":1152213,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30340178a20211fa191d92e377d5a2df5195f11f","tid":1152213,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T23:50:38.000Z","msg":"你未計佢超支"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"超支應該由港鐵自付"},{"pid":"149178a5c7bfe64668f45df924283fc64526af98","tid":1152213,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9caa9010410e5a611549643da3859e7f97b5471","tid":1152213,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30340178a20211fa191d92e377d5a2df5195f11f","tid":1152213,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T23:50:38.000Z","msg":"你未計佢超支"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T09:24:35.000Z","msg":"超支應該由港鐵自付"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T09:25:35.000Z","msg":"港鐵最大股東係政府<br />\n政府既錢咪即係市民既錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid